    </equation></item>
    <item id="import-auto-id2624755">The unit of centripetal acceleration is <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>m</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">/</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>s</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>.</item>
